About us

We're here to get you where you need to be.

Elite Rentals is a family owned business serving the metro area with high quality car rentals. 20 years ago we started out with just two passenger cars, and have grown our fleet to 100+ standard, luxury, and commercial vehicles.

We pride ourselves on customer service, whether that is offering you the cleanest and most reliable cars, or delivering a rental car to your home when you can't easily get to us. Whether it's a business trip or an errand, we've got your back.
